INSERT INTO `courses` (`title`, `slug`, `description`, `shortDescription`, `thumbnailUrl`, `category`, `level`, `targetLanguage`, `price`, `originalPrice`, `currency`, `accessType`, `totalModules`, `totalLessons`, `totalDurationMinutes`, `instructorName`, `status`, `publishedAt`, `hasCertificate`, `hasQuizzes`, `hasDownloads`) VALUES
('Path I: Foundations of French Communication', 'path-i-foundations', 'Build your foundation in French communication for the federal public service. This comprehensive course covers essential grammar, vocabulary, and pronunciation for Level A proficiency. Perfect for beginners starting their bilingual journey.', 'Master the fundamentals of French for federal public servants. Build confidence in basic communication skills.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1434030216411-0b793f4b4173?w=800', 'sle_oral', 'beginner', 'french', 29700, 39700, 'CAD', 'one_time', 6, 24, 480, 'Steven Barholere', 'published', NOW(), true, true, true),
('Path II: Oral Communication Essentials', 'path-ii-oral-essentials', 'Develop your oral communication skills for SLE Level B. Focus on conversation fluency, professional vocabulary, and workplace scenarios. Includes interactive exercises and real-world simulations.', 'Achieve oral fluency for Level B SLE. Practice real workplace conversations and scenarios.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?w=800', 'sle_oral', 'intermediate', 'french', 39700, 49700, 'CAD', 'one_time', 8, 32, 640, 'Steven Barholere', 'published', NOW(), true, true, true),
('Path III: Written Expression Mastery', 'path-iii-written-mastery', 'Master written French for the federal workplace. Learn to write professional emails, reports, and briefing notes. Comprehensive grammar review and style guidelines for Level B written proficiency.', 'Excel in written French communication. Master emails, reports, and official documents.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1455390582262-044cdead277a?w=800', 'sle_written', 'intermediate', 'french', 39700, 49700, 'CAD', 'one_time', 8, 32, 640, 'Steven Barholere', 'published', NOW(), true, true, true),
('Path IV: Advanced Oral Proficiency', 'path-iv-advanced-oral', 'Achieve Level C oral proficiency with advanced conversation techniques, complex vocabulary, and nuanced expression. Prepare for high-stakes presentations and negotiations in French.', 'Reach Level C oral excellence. Master complex discussions and executive presentations.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=800', 'sle_oral', 'advanced', 'french', 49700, 59700, 'CAD', 'one_time', 10, 40, 800, 'Steven Barholere', 'published', NOW(), true, true, true),
('Path V: Executive Written Communication', 'path-v-executive-written', 'Elevate your written French to Level C. Master complex document types, executive summaries, and policy writing. Develop a sophisticated writing style for senior leadership roles.', 'Achieve Level C written mastery. Write with executive-level sophistication and precision.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?w=800', 'sle_written', 'advanced', 'french', 49700, 59700, 'CAD', 'one_time', 10, 40, 800, 'Steven Barholere', 'published', NOW(), true, true, true),
('Path VI: Bilingual Excellence Integration', 'path-vi-bilingual-excellence', 'The ultimate integration course combining all SLE competencies. Perfect for those seeking CBC or CCC profiles. Includes exam preparation, mock tests, and personalized feedback sessions.', 'Complete bilingual mastery for CBC/CCC profiles. Full SLE exam preparation included.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800', 'sle_complete', 'advanced', 'both', 59700, 79700, 'CAD', 'one_time', 12, 48, 960, 'Steven Barholere', 'published', NOW(), true, true, true);
